title: Value displayed by call to doSomething procedure

content.question: PROCEDURE doSomething(num1, num2){DISPLAY(num1)RETURN(num1)DISPLAY(num2)}Consider the following statement.DISPLAY(doSomething(10, 20))What is displayed as a result of executing the statement above?

skill.text: Skill 4.B: Determine the result of code segments.
